# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Prisma — pre-1.0 we skip the migration workflow entirely. schema.prisma
# is the single source of truth; the API boots with `prisma db push` which
# syncs the schema to the DB whether it's empty or already populated.
# Migration files generated locally by `prisma migrate dev` are noise that
# would drift from the runtime behaviour, so we drop them here.
apps/api/prisma/migrations/

